--------------------------------------------------------------------------
def: ^load
is: ^marker
doc:
  Chiller point to command or measure the chiller's load as a percentage
  from "0%" to "100%". When paired with cmd this models the chiller's
  load limit. When paired with sensor this models the chiller's current
  load factor.
